title: Cramer Statement on Veto of National Defense Authorization Act (Kevin Cramer)
text: ( Source : Kevin Cramer ) WASHINGTON, D.C. - Congressman Kevin Cramer made the following statement after President Obama vetoed H.R. 1735, the National Defense Authorization Act ( NDAA ) for FY 2016. The conferenced bill passed the House on Oct.
